.Vb 1
\&  $strEncoding = $doc\->encoding();
.Ve
.Sp
returns the encoding string of the document.
.Sp
.Vb 2
\&  my $doc = XML::LibXML\->createDocument( "1.0", "ISO\-8859\-15" );
