encoding), 'UTF\-8' is returned.
.Sp
.Vb 2
\&  my $doc = XML::LibXML\->createDocument( "1.0", "ISO\-8859\-15" );
\&  print $doc\->encoding; # prints ISO\-8859\-15
.Ve
